com.ece.superkids.questions

Class FileQuestionDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ece.superkids.questions.FileQuestionDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuestionDatabase

    public class FileQuestionDatabase
extends Object
implements QuestionDatabase
    The FileQuestionDatabase loads questions that are stored in JSON format from files on the local file system. The default questions are read only but custom questions are editable.
    Author:
    Ben Duong
